---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy"
  description="Salongroei's cookie policy. Learn which cookies we use and why."
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content" class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <article class="prose-legal">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">
        Cookie Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-expert-navy/50 dark:text-white/50 text-sm mb-12">
        Last updated: January 2025
      </p>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          Cookies are small text files that a website places on your computer, tablet, or phone when you visit the site. They are widely used to make websites work properly, improve efficiency, and provide information to website owners.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">2. Which Cookies Do We Use?</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We distinguish between the following categories of cookies:
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-expert-navy/5 dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-3">
              ðŸŸ¢ Necessary Cookies
            </h3>
            <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              These cookies are essential for the website to function. Without them, certain features cannot work. No consent is required for these cookies.
            </p>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full text-sm text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b border-expert-navy/10 dark:border-white/10">
                    <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Cookie</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Purpose</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-2 font-bold text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Duration</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr class="border-b border-expert-navy/5 dark:border-white/5">
                    <td class="py-2 pr-4">cookie_consent</td>
                    <td class="py-2 pr-4">Remembers your cookie preferences</td>
                    <td class="py-2">12 months</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-expert-navy/5 dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-3">
              ðŸ“Š Analytical Cookies
            </h3>
            <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              These cookies help us understand how visitors use our website. The data is processed anonymously. We use Google Analytics 4 with the following privacy-friendly settings:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed space-y-1 mb-4">
              <li>IP anonymization is enabled by default</li>
              <li>Data is not shared with other Google services</li>
              <li>Retention period set to a maximum of 14 months</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full text-sm text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b border-expert-navy/10 dark:border-white/10">
                    <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Cookie</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Purpose</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-2 font-bold text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Duration</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr class="border-b border-expert-navy/5 dark:border-white/5">
                    <td class="py-2 pr-4">_ga</td>
                    <td class="py-2 pr-4">Distinguishes unique visitors</td>
                    <td class="py-2">2 years</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-expert-navy/5 dark:border-white/5">
                    <td class="py-2 pr-4">_ga_*</td>
                    <td class="py-2 pr-4">Maintains session state</td>
                    <td class="py-2">2 years</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          In addition to our own cookies, third parties may also place cookies via our website, specifically Google Analytics (see above). We do not embed social media widgets or advertising tracking on our website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">4. Your Consent</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          On your first visit to our website, we ask for your consent to place non-essential cookies (analytical cookies). You can change your preferences at any time.
        </p>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          Necessary cookies are always placed regardless of your choice, as they are essential for the website to function.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">5. Managing and Deleting Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          You can manage or delete cookies through your browser settings. Below you'll find instructions for the most commonly used browsers:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
          <li><a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Chrome</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/clear-cookies-and-site-data-firefox" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mozilla Firefox</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-sfri11471/mac" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Safari</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/delete-cookies-in-microsoft-edge-63947406-40ac-c3b8-57b9-2a946a29ae09" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Microsoft Edge</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Please note: blocking or deleting cookies may cause certain website features to not work optimally.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">6. Changes</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          We may update this cookie policy from time to time, for example when we add new cookies or modify existing ones. The most recent version is always available on this page.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">7. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          Do you have questions about our cookie policy? Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@salongroei.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@salongroei.com</a>. Also see our <a href="/en/privacy" class="text-primary hover:underline">privacy policy</a> for more information about the processing of personal data.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
